&lt;li&gt;Deploy, configure, and operate containerized workloads on Kubernetes using Helm charts; manage cluster lifecycle, namespaces, RBAC, and networking policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain Docker images and container registries; enforce image security scanning and vulnerability remediation within the pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
