&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Intro:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zephyr provides test management capabilities to Atlassian products, working as a plugin/extension for Jira and Confluence, for managing both manual and automated testing processes. Using AI, users can transform their manual tests into automated tests and accelerate their delivery cycles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://marketplace.atlassian.com/apps/1213259/zephyr-test-management-and-automation-for-jira&quot;&gt;Atlassian Marketplace&lt;/a&gt; is the main distribution channel of Zephyr. Having great success over the years, Zephyr is one of the top-selling apps in the Atlassian Marketplace, experiencing huge growth with more than hundreds of thousands of monthly active users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From an engineering perspective, we use native Cloud solutions on AWS, deploying multiple times a day, and using microservices. Our high-performance team of engineers use many of the modern good practices for software development, such as (a lot of) test automation, test-driven development (TDD), continuous delivery, progressive rollouts and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please, visit our product page if you want to know more about&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://smartbear.com/test-management/zephyr/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Zephyr&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
